<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Business Spew — API Access</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.ico">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(150deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #2c3e50 60%, #1a3a4a 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #ecf0f1;
      padding: 0 0 80px;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px 36px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.2em;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      color: #fff;
    }

    header p {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    header a { color: #00ffcc; text-decoration: none; }
    header a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* ── Section headings ─────────────────────────────── */
    h2 {
      font-size: 0.72em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    /* ── Cards ────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .card {
      background: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.85);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    /* ── Body text ────────────────────────────────────── */
    p {
      font-size: 0.95em;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* ── Steps ────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .steps {
      counter-reset: steps;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .steps li {
      counter-increment: steps;
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 0.93em;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    }

    .steps li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .steps li::before {
      content: counter(steps);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.82em;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .steps li strong { color: #fff; }

    /* ── Route list ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .route-list {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .route-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      font-size: 0.88em;
    }

    .route-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .method {
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.78em;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      min-width: 46px;
      text-align: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .method.get  { background: #27ae60; color: #fff; }
    .method.post { background: #e67e22; color: #fff; }

    .route-path {
      font-family: monospace;
      color: #00ffcc;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      min-width: 280px;
    }

    .route-desc {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 0.95em;
    }

    /* ── Base URL block ───────────────────────────────── */
    .base-url {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      border-left: 3px solid #00ffcc;
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.95em;
      color: #00ffcc;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .base-url span {
      display: block;
      font-family: sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.75em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    /* ── CTA ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 24px;
    }

    .cta p {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.95em;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: #2980b9; }

    /* ── Footer ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      font-size: 0.82em;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }

    footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .route-path  { min-width: unset; }
      .route-desc  { display: none; }
      .route-list li { flex-wrap: wrap; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Business Spew 🔥 — API Access</h1>
  <p>
    <a href="https://leveragedsynergies.com">About</a>
    &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
    <a href="https://bs.leveragedsynergies.com">Playground</a>
    &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
    <a href="https://bs.leveragedsynergies.com/api-docs">Full API Docs</a>
  </p>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="card">
    <h2>About the API</h2>
    <p>
      The Business Spew API generates corporate jargon on demand across multiple
      vocabulary topics. It is available to approved developers and integrators.
      Access is controlled by API key — issued personally and revocable at any time.
    </p>
    <p>
      There is no charge for access. There is no SLA. There is, however, an
      inexhaustible supply of synergy playbooks and stakeholder maps.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>How to Request Access</h2>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>
        <strong>Contact the maintainer</strong> — reach out via
        [<!-- TODO: add contact method, e.g. email link or form -->]
        and briefly describe your intended use.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Receive your API key</strong> — keys are issued manually and
        tied to an owner. Keep yours private; do not commit it to source control.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Include the key in every request</strong> — pass it as an HTTP
        header: <code style="font-family:monospace; color:#00ffcc;">X-API-Key: your-key-here</code>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Start generating</strong> — point your client at the base URL
        below and choose a route.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Base URL</h2>
    <div class="base-url">
      <span>All API requests</span>
      https://api.leveragedsynergies.com
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 20px;">Available Routes</h2>
    <ul class="route-list">
      <li>
        <span class="method get">GET</span>
        <span class="route-path">/api</span>
        <span class="route-desc">Service status and loaded topics — no key required</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="method get">GET</span>
        <span class="route-path">/api/:topic</span>
        <span class="route-desc">Generate spew for a named topic</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="method get">GET</span>
        <span class="route-path">/api/:topic/:sentences?/:paragraphs?/:title?</span>
        <span class="route-desc">Generate with optional parameters</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="method get">GET</span>
        <span class="route-path">/api/:sentences?/:paragraphs?/:title?</span>
        <span class="route-desc">Random topic, optional parameters</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="method post">POST</span>
        <span class="route-path">/spew</span>
        <span class="route-desc">Generate via JSON request body</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="method get">GET</span>
        <span class="route-path">/health</span>
        <span class="route-desc">Liveness check — no key required</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card cta">
    <p>Want to explore the full parameter reference and example responses?</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="https://bs.leveragedsynergies.com/api-docs">
      View Full API Documentation &rarr;
    </a>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  <p>In memory of Wilson A. Rogers &nbsp;|&nbsp; <%= app_version %> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    <a href="https://leveragedsynergies.com">Leveraged Synergies</a>
  </p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
